{"tid":1217094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娥本人","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:58:49.000Z","uid":123111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1452f712340f413006c5a01dad4842761d01d757","tid":1217094,"uid":123111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"有無人記得毛記電視首娥本人<br />\n<br />\n《娥本人》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：《我本人》，吳雨霏<br />\n改詞：毛記電視<br />\n主唱：Carrie（盤菜瑩子聲演）<br />\n<br />\n連上帝也知我潛能 還讓我舐晒渣梁粉<br />\n份List好長 人人也畀面 係爭 沒有泛民<br />\n田大少也即將變心<br />\n<br />\n其實個法官是閒人 其實我討厭渣薯粉<br />\n葉劉Baby 葡萄到傷身 弱得 像個廢人<br />\n誰像我識對祖國氹一氹<br />\n<br />\n傻㗎你 聽邊個誤傳林鄭害你哋<br />\n你班人 其實故宮好好㗎夾硬起<br />\n唔Gur你 膽仔咁大隨時能溶埋你<br />\n娥本人 連入閘機都畀我入嚟<br />\n娥本人 其實未L使驚你負皮<br />\n娥本人 其實就好打得過趙薇<br />\n娥本人 其實勁喜歡中國國旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9106f4b0d75c00eeb43c5ec7edcfbeb1d9d2f9","tid":1217094,"uid":123111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}